name: Artifact Rocklin (contained)
description:
Rocklin's are TYPICALLY everywhere you go!

But these infernal little beasts are hiding in the deepest depths of our precious little bubble,

only poking their heads up into society every now and then to cause the worst stubbed toe.

Keep Your Toes SAFE! 

Rocklin's must be contained for their own good!

These need to be captured in a special box.

(special box included)
